name: Is This Art?
description:
Is This Art?
I didn't paint it.
I didn't photograph it.
I typed words into an app on my iPhone.
5 minutes later the app returned this image.
Which words...?
Perhaps THAT is the Art?
Should you buy it...?
Yeah... I think you should.
